page.title: 04Wildlife
page.content: There is quite alot of{wildlife}in our area.Plenty has been seen and heard. The main of these must be{birds.}This is list of some of them:{Sparrow {kestrels,Nuthatch,Robin,Sparrowhawk, {Blackbird,Yellowhammer,magpie,Mallard, {Pied wagtail,Tree creeper,Jay,Jackdaw, {Crow,rook,carion crow,doves, pigeons, {Partridge, pheasant,lapwing,woodcock, {Goldcrest,thrushes, wren,lark, owls, {Tits, finches.}There is a{pond.}In it we have{amphibians}such as{Frogs,Toads and{Newts. Reptiles}in the area are {Lizard,Slowworm,and Snakes.}Small {mammals,}are{Mice,Rats,Voles,Moles, {Shrews,Hedgehogs,Hares,Badgers,Rabbits {Weasles,stoats and Squirrels.}Larger {mammals}are{Fox,Fallow Roe and Muntjak deer.There are the usual sorts of{bugs including{spiders, woodlice, beetles, {flying insects like bees and wasps, {ants,crickets}and various{molluscs.
